{"tid":2070580,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"請勿接HKUE的暑期工","createTime":"2020-06-19T08:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T02:49:23.000Z","uid":230641,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b30fd36fd283c87951983b263e1dd98573002f3","tid":2070580,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UyzkBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UyzkBm.png&h=3dbc4d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，HKUE嘅臭名連登隨便搵就有<br />\n如果做呢份工，你要賣良心比公司，搵人嚟讀啲冇認受性嘅課程。"},{"pid":"0c53c913c579302744b4479ad46c3d6297980ff5","tid":2070580,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7537d47d7c91e6ed39c7713ae7603986d0aabdd0","tid":2070580,"uid":247338,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6b30fd36fd283c87951983b263e1dd98573002f3","tid":2070580,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UyzkBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UyzkBm.png&h=3dbc4d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，HKUE嘅臭名連登隨便搵就有<br />\n如果做呢份工，你要賣良心比公司，搵人嚟讀啲冇認受性嘅課程。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"推   專出美容雞  傳銷狗  既hkue  周圍去呃人錢"},{"pid":"d98fb8fdc6d66f66304700257b0ba2bb35c3aae8","tid":2070580,"uid":7828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span style=\"color: green;\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=2daeb140\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=deac77c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=d7febbfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e33624a681