/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"騙徒Crystal Li李婉瑩新電話號碼: 91570141<br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n更多資訊： <br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=224af3fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=11d6778d\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f44ohbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff44ohbs.jpg&h=a018e3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VbXiY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VbXiY9.jpg&h=a59da781&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModKJqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModKJqQ.jpg&h=a38f4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢部分冇p圖嘅真樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOkHOCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOkHOCZ.jpg&h=f279000e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mSK1X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mSK1X0.jpg&h=be2c20d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係條女部分聲音 Backup <br />\n<br />\n同人plan 升學路線? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-24&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=4340cc33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24</a> <br />\n<br />\n想叫我個fd上去 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-30&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=9782634d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-30</a> <br />\n<br />\n番工幫到人? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-31&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=18da4c5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-31</a> <br />\n<br />\n幫DSE 學生? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-23-12-36-35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-07-23-12-36-35&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=f75c7c52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-23-12-36-35</a> <br />\n<br />\n自稱讀電影v1 <br />\n<a href=\"https://so